{"tid":1618082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個 慢慢被香港人遺忘嘅事情","createTime":"2019-10-04T04:01:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T04:20:42.000Z","uid":32665,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"711b40e51c9b1593fe44e3fb61371d26cab662a4","tid":1618082,"uid":32665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:01:19.000Z","msg":"殺人政權<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FUDRDf7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFUDRDf7.jpg&h=dcf76107&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n6月15日 下午4時半，一名35歲姓梁男子於金鐘道太古廣場平台危站，他身穿黃衣外套，掛起「反送中No Extradition To China」的橫額，上面亦寫有「全面撤回送中，我們不是暴動，釋放學生傷者，林鄭下台，Help Hong Kong」的訴求標語。近9時許，男子突然往外爬出棚架，其間4名消防員嘗試將男子拉回不果，男子上衣被拉脫後突然墮下，他被送往律敦治醫院搶救後證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n梁生係令我係依場運動 一直走落去嘅原因之一<br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822e31211b692df104d7a53d495d60f88f4633ad","tid":1618082,"uid":107898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:05:58.000Z","msg":"無<br />\n每件事每個人都記喺心中"},{"pid":"fb012f2bdab8544dfcef86c00f0ac0e36ca92e4b","tid":1618082,"uid":32665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6594008160f473cf17610beb50150c133fe2689","tid":1618082,"uid":300323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:20:42.000Z","msg":"無人遺忘啊屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}